Its high inbuilt short circuit breaking capacity across theentire model line, its flexible AC and DC application and its approval and compliance in accordance with all major international and local standards make it truly unique.All current System pro M compact® accessories can be combined easily with the new model line. Whether warehousing or project engineering, planning, installing or maintaining your equipment, the S 200 M UC is a simple and flexible solution.
